767
00:55:04.625 --> 00:55:08.183
<font color="#00ffff">Damien is the best boy in the world.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">isn't he?</font>

768
00:55:08.185 --> 00:55:10.025
<font color="#ffffff">We'll do our best</font>
