769
00:55:20.265 --> 00:55:22.823
<font color="#ffffff">Her clothes had been washed</font>
<font color="#ffffff">and dried.</font>

770
00:55:22.825 --> 00:55:24.705
<font color="#ffffff">She'd been kept somewhere.</font>

771
00:55:30.225 --> 00:55:32.345
<font color="#ffffff">I'm thinking. perhaps?</font>

772
00:55:46.665 --> 00:55:49.825
<font color="#ffff00">Ready? </font><font color="#ffffff">Ready.</font>

773
00:56:06.265 --> 00:56:07.825
<font color="#ffffff">Oh. Katy.</font>

774
00:56:09.145 --> 00:56:10.705
<font color="#ffffff">Oh. Christ.</font>

